gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n平啲都要一百蚊港紙一餐"},{"pid":"1121c0d489b065c004e6dc427e747efa29d426f0","tid":474693,"uid":5547,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T12:42:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>剩駛一日80鎊<br />\n酒店未計</blockquote><br />\n唔計住呢<br />\n食嘢係咪普遍都貴唔特別搵平嘢食嘅話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你想點玩先？<br />\nSOHO區30鎊6隻生蠔加白酒<br />\nBorough market 10鎊10隻即湯生蠔<br />\n普通pub 一個pie加杯野飲 廿鎊<br />\n整杯雪糕 3鎊<br />\n唐人街其實抵食過香港 仲要勁多真正舊港式風味<br />\n想extreme中東佬4鎊duner實食到你飽<br />\n自己諗下點玩"},{"pid":"e3ee38a24fd0a49f7d42a312af98debeb23d1f75","tid":474693,"uid":89595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T12:49:20.000Z","msg":"去咗六日<br />\n上埋Birmingham 用咗千三蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搭tube真係好春貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"837ecdadd1e041a9fe6729a706acaa11a13160f8","tid":474693,"uid":120850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T12:51:09.000Z","msg":"計食計答車<br />\n二三十磅一日"},{"pid":"4d5842aa32d674c70f752baa711a041a4cb95434","tid":474693,"uid":55732,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T14:19:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>剩駛一日80鎊<br />\n酒店未計</blockquote><br />\n唔計住呢<br />\n食嘢係咪普遍都貴唔特別搵平嘢食嘅話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你想點玩先？<br />\nSOHO區30鎊6隻生蠔加白酒<br />\nBorough market 10鎊10隻即湯生蠔<br />\n普通pub 一個pie加杯野飲 廿鎊<br />\n整杯雪糕 3鎊<br />\n唐人街其實抵食過香港 仲要勁多真正舊港式風味<br />\n想extreme中東佬4鎊duner實食到你飽<br />\n自己諗下點玩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唐人街旺記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冇錢嗰陣真係當佢救星<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n燒味雙拼飯 5鎊80p就搞掂<br />\n不過味道就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n啲日本餐就有平有貴<br />\neat Tokyo嗰啲便當10－15鎊但基本上食到你滯<br />\n相似option仲可以食下意粉或者越南河粉嘅，連鎖店咩Bella Italia嗰啲淨嗌意粉嘅話係咁嘅rate<br />\n金田家，一風堂嗰啲拉麵店就15-20鎊左右（不過去英國旅行無理由食拉麵掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<br />\n最extreme應該係去超市買sandwich meal deal 3鎊包三文治，細薯片同汽水，平過麥記餐，當然餐餐咁食嘅話，你嘅旅途會染上一層灰色，尤其是冬天食<br />\n<br />\n另外想慳嘅話仲有好多options嘅，尤其是快餐嗰啲。土炮嗰啲咩Leon或者West Cornwall pasty，Wasabi <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Itsu <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  嗰啲都可以做到10鎊以內有交易<br />\n<br />\n想食好少少嘅話，我諗30鎊一餐就無走雞，不過如果你係去旅行而且budget鬆動嘅話，食嗰方面預多啲會好啲，因為我上面講嗰堆有唔少真係窮遊/嗰邊讀書先會諗"},{"pid":"c71a5881788c2ddda2e73f55e6e3f2b099251fa3","tid":474693,"uid":23758,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T14:36:50.000Z","msg":"手信呢"},{"pid":"334de8d37101425aa070ed1e3d3ee39fba149eb2","tid":474693,"uid":45431,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T15:32:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>剩駛一日80鎊<br />\n酒店未計</blockquote><br />\n唔計住呢<br />\n食嘢係咪普遍都貴唔特別搵平嘢食嘅話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你想點玩先？<br />\nSOHO區30鎊6隻生蠔加白酒<br />\nBorough market 10鎊10隻即湯生蠔<br />\n普通pub 一個pie加杯野飲 廿鎊<br />\n整杯雪糕 3鎊<br />\n唐人街其實抵食過香港 仲要勁多真正舊港式風味<br />\n想extreme中東佬4鎊duner實食到你飽<br />\n自己諗下點玩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唐人街旺記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冇錢嗰陣真係當佢救星<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n燒味雙拼飯 5鎊80p就搞掂<br />\n不過味道就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n啲日本餐就有平有貴<br />\neat Tokyo嗰啲便當10－15鎊但基本上食到你滯<br />\n相似option仲可以食下意粉或者越南河粉嘅，連鎖店咩Bella Italia嗰啲淨嗌意粉嘅話係咁嘅rate<br />\n金田家，一風堂嗰啲拉麵店就15-20鎊左右（不過去英國旅行無理由食拉麵掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<br />\n最extreme應該係去超市買sandwich meal deal 3鎊包三文治，細薯片同汽水，平過麥記餐，當然餐餐咁食嘅話，你嘅旅途會染上一層灰色，尤其是冬天食<br />\n<br />\n另外想慳嘅話仲有好多options嘅，尤其是快餐嗰啲。土炮嗰啲咩Leon或者West Cornwall pasty，Wasabi <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Itsu <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  嗰啲都可以做到10鎊以內有交易<br />\n<br />\n想食好少少嘅話，我諗30鎊一餐就無走雞，不過如果你係去旅行而且budget鬆動嘅話，食嗰方面預多啲會好啲，因為我上面講嗰堆有唔少真係窮遊/嗰邊讀書先會諗</blockquote><br />\n其實就算一餐百幾鎊都係難食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n倫敦食飽算架啦，留返錢玩啦"},{"pid":"9145c49a24b883a292c8c88ce5adc2e21bc876b8","tid":474693,"uid":34509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T15:48:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>計食計答車<br />\n二三十磅一日</blockquote><br />\n我個陣去每日搭車都搭到張oyster card既每日收費上限<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁就可以瘋狂乜撚都搭一餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eeaf611491ca32a5c9672c120d7fe20f71b4ae95","tid":474693,"uid":5547,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T22:52:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>剩駛一日80鎊<br />\n酒店未計</blockquote><br />\n唔計住呢<br />\n食嘢係咪普遍都貴唔特別搵平嘢食嘅話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你想點玩先？<br />\nSOHO區30鎊6隻生蠔加白酒<br />\nBorough market 10鎊10隻即湯生蠔<br />\n普通pub 一個pie加杯野飲 廿鎊<br />\n整杯雪糕 3鎊<br />\n唐人街其實抵食過香港 仲要勁多真正舊港式風味<br />\n想extreme中東佬4鎊duner實食到你飽<br />\n自己諗下點玩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唐人街旺記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冇錢嗰陣真係當佢救星<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n燒味雙拼飯 5鎊80p就搞掂<br />\n不過味道就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n啲日本餐就有平有貴<br />\neat Tokyo嗰啲便當10－15鎊但基本上食到你滯<br />\n相似option仲可以食下意粉或者越南河粉嘅，連鎖店咩Bella Italia嗰啲淨嗌意粉嘅話係咁嘅rate<br />\n金田家，一風堂嗰啲拉麵店就15-20鎊左右（不過去英國旅行無理由食拉麵掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<br />\n最extreme應該係去超市買sandwich meal deal 3鎊包三文治，細薯片同汽水，平過麥記餐，當然餐餐咁食嘅話，你嘅旅途會染上一層灰色，尤其是冬天食<br />\n<br />\n另外想慳嘅話仲有好多options嘅，尤其是快餐嗰啲。土炮嗰啲咩Leon或者West Cornwall pasty，Wasabi <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Itsu <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  嗰啲都可以做到10鎊以內有交易<br />\n<br />\n想食好少少嘅話，我諗30鎊一餐就無走雞，不過如果你係去旅行而且budget鬆動嘅話，食嗰方面預多啲會好啲，因為我上面講嗰堆有唔少真係窮遊/嗰邊讀書先會諗</blockquote><br />\n其實就算一餐百幾鎊都係難食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n倫敦食飽算架啦，留返錢玩啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔覺難食"},{"pid":"c6b92c6e35b33033134a3acf8b1399df1c97af68","tid":474693,"uid":47041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T23:51:29.000Z","msg":"六月去兩個人洗左8k左右<br />\n未計機票住宿波飛<br />\n買左張7day travelcard任搭<br />\n景點用2for1<br />\n參加左個溫沙堡 bath 巨石一日團<br />\n食野就無咩點就算食<br />\n不過都無食好高檔既野<br />\n純買紀念品同手信"},{"pid":"bbd27cecd231d8635cb5c5f93ead973e16775edb","tid":474693,"uid":114692,"like":1,"dislike":12,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T00:03:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f71683e7b6925191d997aed8a82ad901825a3edd","tid":474693,"uid":57488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T00:24:11.000Z","msg":"超市買包食<br />\n1鎊食到幾餐"},{"pid":"3d3bd5159d0dfb4951a6b831880fec3b58604261","tid":474693,"uid":69805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T00:36:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>剩駛一日80鎊<br />\n酒店未計</blockquote><br />\n唔計住呢<br />\n食嘢係咪普遍都貴唔特別搵平嘢食嘅話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你想點玩先？<br />\nSOHO區30鎊