falgar Square Library果堆</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n水鳩人地<br />\n大英博物館 半日都行完 <br />\nHMS 同 tower bridge 要一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e50bf3efac30b7c69a615d76ac0375f980882486","tid":474693,"uid":5547,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T16:39:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>倫敦點玩到一個禮拜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n去打卡上facebook果D死MK就緊係唔得<br />\n去睇文化歷史野14曰都搞唔店啦<br />\n<br />\n一日Tower of London<br />\n一日Windsor Castle<br />\n一至兩日British Museum<br />\n一日Imperial War Museum<br />\n一日RAF Museum<br />\n一日HMS Belfast, Tower Bridge<br />\n半日肥佬吉個War Room<br />\n一日過Salisbury Stonehenge / Bath<br />\n未計Borough market 唐人街 Trafalgar Square Library果堆</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n水鳩人地<br />\n大英博物館 半日都行完 <br />\nHMS 同 tower bridge 要一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你行Museum字都唔睇 Voice guide又唔聽咁你入去屙個尿影張相就搞店啦屌你<br />\n大英博物館你認真睇認真聽跟本無可能係48個鐘行哂睇哂<br />\n水乜撚野呀? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a915616135c7d84cdc9dd2e42911da8bc658d678","tid":474693,"uid":114692,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T17:22:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ec1ed017ddfcedc670f9d87c5a8ba26da792a787","tid":474693,"uid":72702,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T09:02:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>倫敦點玩到一個禮拜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n去打卡上facebook果D死MK就緊係唔得<br />\n去睇文化歷史野14曰都搞唔店啦<br />\n<br />\n一日Tower of London<br />\n一日Windsor Castle<br />\n一至兩日British Museum<br />\n一日Imperial War Museum<br />\n一日RAF Museum<br />\n一日HMS Belfast, Tower Bridge<br />\n半日肥佬吉個War Room<br />\n一日過Salisbury Stonehenge / Bath<br />\n未計Borough market 唐人街 Trafalgar Square Library果堆</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n水鳩人地<br />\n大英博物館 半日都行完 <br />\nHMS 同 tower bridge 要一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nD博物館好悶<br />\n全英最正都係大自然博物館<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n老實講人人喜好唔同，我啱嘅你都未必啱，如果你你係check point型咁去旅行，到此一遊就夠嘅，咁七日對你嚟講當然係太多啦<br />\n但倫敦其實幾多地方去博物館一大堆，歌劇又一大堆，教堂等歷史建築又多，仲未計近郊嗰啲地方<br />\n我上次去左七日真係唔夠用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3606296e25d9d178927cfb158be7943e4a9365c8","tid":474693,"uid":5547,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T09:14:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>倫敦點玩到一個禮拜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n去打卡上facebook果D死MK就緊係唔得<br />\n去睇文化歷史野14曰都搞唔店啦<br />\n<br />\n一日Tower of London<br />\n一日Windsor Castle<br />\n一至兩日British Museum<br />\n一日Imperial War Museum<br />\n一日RAF Museum<br />\n一日HMS Belfast, Tower Bridge<br />\n半日肥佬吉個War Room<br />\n一日過Salisbury Stonehenge / Bath<br />\n未計Borough market 唐人街 Trafalgar Square Library果堆</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n水鳩人地<br />\n大英博物館 半日都行完 <br />\nHMS 同 tower bridge 要一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nD博物館好悶<br />\n全英最正都係大自然博物館<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n老實講人人喜好唔同，我啱嘅你都未必啱，如果你你係check point型咁去旅行，到此一遊就夠嘅，咁七日對你嚟講當然係太多啦<br />\n但倫敦其實幾多地方去博物館一大堆，歌劇又一大堆，教堂等歷史建築又多，仲未計近郊嗰啲地方<br />\n我上次去左七日真係唔夠用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n柏林慕尼黑維也納都一樣道理<br />\n如果佢地唔識欣賞堆歷史文化建築音樂等等<br />\n咪一兩日就話悶<br />\n我同你講一個博物館可以睇足一日都唔夠<br />\n係好正常既事<br />\n慕尼黑個德意志科學館<br />\n柏林既德意志歷史館<br />\n倫敦既大英博物館<br />\n維也納既奧地利戰爭館<br />\n呢幾個我都係一開門就鳩衝睇到比人趕扯都睇唔到60% <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1ee5039926620237012dcf8f9f5f8431fe742cf","tid":474693,"uid":7814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T16:38:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>倫敦點玩到一個禮拜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n去打卡上facebook果D死MK就緊係唔得<br />\n去睇文化歷史野14曰都搞唔店啦<br />\n<br />\n一日Tower of London<br />\n一日Windsor Castle<br />\n一至兩日British Museum<br />\n一日Imperial War Museum<br />\n一日RAF Museum<br />\n一日HMS Belfast, Tower Bridge<br />\n半日肥佬吉個War Room<br />\n一日過Salisbury Stonehenge / Bath<br />\n未計Borough market 唐人街 Trafalgar Square Library果堆</blockquote><br />\nbath 都算london 咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd9f1ba73671b27557ac5a567b41ee27eedf5e1c","tid":474693,"uid":65298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T16:45:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>倫敦點玩到一個禮拜<img src=\"/assets/fac